{
  "stem": "5626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BEEP]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1945.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, we were liberated by the American Army and--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I mentioned it before, that we were standing in a corner of a barrack, and saying our Friday-night prayers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when the first soldier came in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one came in a American uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember he had a white glove on, and this light beige uniform, and the army cap, put to the side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was smiling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And suddenly, he was speaking Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We don't know what's his name was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We couldn't get to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said that from now on, you are free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you are free.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of us?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, all of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where are the Germans?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, you don't have to worry about the German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are taking care of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just go back to your barrack, sit down like we are not here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just be happy that the Germans are not here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And wait till next morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we will tell you-- we will give you further instructions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't think there was one person who slept that night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were just talking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know what to talk about it, talk the past or talk the future.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew the past.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was very sad and very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't know what the future is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We still knew-- hear that the war is on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The army group which came to us, they were just a occupation unit, or whatever you call it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were-- [? passed by us. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This ?] same Hungarian-speaking soldier came and explained to us that we had to go in our barracks at night because they were rounding up the Germans within to camp and outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
